// OpenLayers complete exercise

// BASICS 30'
//     +Create a full screen map
//     +Set projection to 900913 and displayProjection to 4326
//     +Restrict the map extent of the map to a bounding box (coordinates must be in 900913)
//     +Add two raster layers as overlays (mapquest and the states layer from geoserver)
//     +Set tilesize to 512 * 512
//     +Load the geoserver wms layer with singleTile (see the different labeling options)
//     +Set the transparency of a layer to 50%
//     +Add the layerswitcher
//     +Avoid the OSM layer to appear in the layerSwitcher
//     +Add the zoombox control
//     +Add the mouseposition control

